OL,3,C60,000 fines worth #6m issued to Kent
OL,4,Cdrivers as speed limit changes
OL,6,FA leading MP and a firm of specialist
OL,7,Fdefence lawyers have backed angry
OL,8,Fmotorists calling for the cancellation
OL,9,Fof millions of pounds worth of
OL,10,Fspeeding fines issued on a Kent road
OL,11,Fin just six weeks.JSpeed cameras on
OL,12,Fthe A20 between Sidcup and Swanley
OL,13,Ftriggered more than 60,000 fines after
OL,14,Fthe limit was suddenly lowered from
OL,15,F70mph to 40mph.
OL,17,FDrivers claim the signs at Crittals
OL,18,FCorner were so small that they didn't
OL,19,Fnotice them and their Sat Navs were
OL,20,Fstill showing the original limits.
