OL,4,Cdrivers as speed limit changes
OL,6,FDrivers along that stretch of the A20
OL,7,Fhave been issued with 49,000 tickets
OL,8,Fin the last year.
OL,10,FBut, in the last six weeks alone, the
OL,11,Fcameras issued 62,000 fines.
OL,13,FThousands of people have taken to
OL,14,Fsocial media to protest saying the
OL,15,Fchange happened without prior warning
OL,16,Fand inadequate signage.
OL,18,FThe cameras have caught so many
OL,19,Fdrivers out, it's become the most
OL,20,Fprolific speed camera in the UK.
