OL,6,FThe total cost of speeding fines
OL,7,Ffollowing the speed change on this
OL,8,Froad has now surpassed #6m.
OL,10,FSome of the cases have been taken up
OL,11,Fby a legal firm specialising in
OL,12,Fmotoring law.
OL,14,FSince the six week period of the
OL,15,F62,000 fines, the signage has been
OL,16,Fimproved.
