OL,6,FIn a statement issued by Transport for
OL,7,FLondon in February, a spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Safety is our number one
OL,9,Fpriority and we have temporarily
OL,10,Fintroduced a 40mph speed limit on the
OL,11,FA20 Sidcup Road due to ongoing surface
OL,12,Fwater flooding which has caused a
OL,13,Fnumber of safety concerns and serious
OL,14,Frisk to road users.
OL,16,F"The reduced speed limit has been
OL,17,Fintroduced in response to that risk.
